    <item>
      <title>拜登将边境法案失败归咎于特朗普，乌克兰悬而未决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/biden-pins-border-bill-failure-on-trump-leaving-ukraine-hanging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登指责唐纳德·特朗普否决了两党移民和乌克兰援助法案，称这位共和党领跑者向他的党内成员施压，要求他们拒绝该法案，以便在11月的选举中获得优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/biden-pins-border-bill-failure-on-trump-leaving-ukraine-hanging</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 18:39:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普被剥夺刑事指控豁免权后的下一步是什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/is-trump-going-on-trial-what-to-know-after-court-rejected-immunity-claim</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 在上诉法院就其是否免于起诉的问题上败诉，这让他在再次竞选总统之际，又因试图推翻 2020 年大选而受到审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/is-trump-going-on-trial-what-to-know-after-court-rejected-immunity-claim</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:49:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡塔尔称哈马斯对人质谈判做出了“积极”回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/qatar-says-hamas-sent-positive-response-over-hostage-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔总理表示，巴勒斯坦激进组织哈马斯对停止加沙地带战斗以换取释放部分以色列人质的提议做出了“积极”回应，这为尽快达成协议带来了希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/qatar-says-hamas-sent-positive-response-over-hostage-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:37:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示，巴西总统卢拉就职第二年，支持率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/brazil-s-lula-starts-second-year-with-popularity-on-the-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的民意调查显示，巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦开启了他的第二年任期，在经济表现超出预期后，超过一半的巴西人认可了他的工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/brazil-s-lula-starts-second-year-with-popularity-on-the-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:04:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莱辛表示，哈佛商学院毕业生对校友投票感到“困惑”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/harvard-business-grads-confused-over-alumni-vote-lessin-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年未能成功加入哈佛大学校友会的风险投资家萨姆·莱辛(Sam Lessin)对这一过程表示担忧，他说这阻碍了人们的参与。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/harvard-business-grads-confused-over-alumni-vote-lessin-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国船舶获得更便宜的保险以航行红海</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/chinese-ships-get-cheaper-insurance-to-navigate-houthi-menaced-red-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国商船在穿越红海时获得大幅保险折扣，这是胡塞武装在该地区的袭击正在损害与西方有联系的船只商业利益的另一个迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/chinese-ships-get-cheaper-insurance-to-navigate-houthi-menaced-red-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 16:55:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒默推动步履蹒跚的美国边境-乌克兰协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/schumer-presses-ahead-on-faltering-us-border-ukraine-aid-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默本周将就一项两党协议进行测试投票，该协议旨在实施新的美国边境限制并解锁乌克兰战争援助，尽管共和党的反对声音越来越大，几乎肯定会否决该措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/schumer-presses-ahead-on-faltering-us-border-ukraine-aid-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 16:18:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟试图将美国的绿色补贴与其清洁技术协议相匹配</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/eu-reaches-clean-tech-deal-to-answer-the-us-tax-credit-system</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟达成了一项临时协议，以支持其清洁技术产业，以应对来自美国和中国的全球挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/eu-reaches-clean-tech-deal-to-answer-the-us-tax-credit-system</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 16:13:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新罕布什尔州初选前的拜登音频 Deepfake 追踪到德克萨斯州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/new-hampshire-authorities-trace-biden-audio-deepfake-to-texas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据新罕布什尔州当局称，一条由人工智能生成的克隆总统乔·拜登的音频信息试图劝阻登记的民主党人在初选中投票，该信息被追踪到德克萨斯州的一家公司及其所有者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/new-hampshire-authorities-trace-biden-audio-deepfake-to-texas</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 15:41:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
